Name:           criu
Version:        4.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Checkpoint/Restore In Userspace Tools
License:        GPL-2.0-only
Group:          System/Console
URL:            https://criu.org/
Source0:        http://github.com/checkpoint-restore/criu/archive/v%{version}.tar.gz#/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
